    "Investigating semisupervised or active learning methods may also help use unlabeled data effectively, improving model robustness without over-reliance on labeled instances.",
    "• Optimization and Real-Time Adaptability: Developing adaptive models that selfupdate based on new fraud patterns is crucial for CCFD's evolving landscape.",
